ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations (Mexico)
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS (Visa Requirement - Mexico), which will remove Mexico from the list of countries and territories whose citizens are exempt from the temporary resident visa requirement for travel to Canada under subsection 190(1) of the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations.
